        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This *+2 striking warhammer* is inlaid with precious metals and decorated with geometric patterns in a dwarven style. If you\u2019re a dwarf, a *dwarven thrower* functions for you as a *+2 greater striking returning warhammer* with the thrown 30 feet trait, and your attacks with the hammer deal 1d8 additional damage against giants.",
